title: GET_LAST_PED_IN_VEHICLE_SEAT
content:
0xF7C6792D// GetLastPedInVehicleSeat
Entity GET_LAST_PED_IN_VEHICLE_SEAT(Vehicle vehicle, int seatIndex);Parameters:vehicle: The target vehicle.seatIndex: See eSeatPosition declared in IS_VEHICLE_SEAT_FREE.Returns: The last ped in the specified seat of the passed vehicle. Returns 0 if the specified seat was never occupied or the last ped does not exist anymore.
